title: NINA - GREAT SUMMER DAY
description: School's out for summer! Help student Nina finish her last math exam - then it's time for fun! The sporty girl loves diving, so meet with her friend at the beach and take part in a diving competition. Can you find all the fish in the ocean? Afterwards, it time for even more fun! Get out of the water and dress Nina up to party. Select a beautiful dress, matching accessories and a lovely hairstyle to finish the look. Your sweetheart is already waiting for you and suprises you with a bunch of flowers. What a great start for summer!
